{"tid":1771643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［民陣遊行］12月8日想見到大家","createTime":"2019-12-06T04:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T06:01:56.000Z","uid":244058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ba7eb2a0ff708a7763c608aa14b552f7e2589d8","tid":1771643,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"12月8日 希望大家一齊黎<br />\n唔好遺忘逝去既手足<br />\n抗爭左六個月啦<br />\n我地得到咩回應？<br />\n<br />\n手足被送中幾千失蹤人口未搵到<br />\n721警方勾結黑社會<br />\n831警方親手殺害市民未公開cctv<br />\n仲有好多好多警暴性侵未追究<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！<br />\n香港人反抗！<br />\n香港人報仇！<br />\n<br />\n希望見到大家 跪求大家一定要黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7Qmwg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7Qmwg1.jpg&h=7ea452d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80172fe84b3b1b3ea937cecaa7900ecc4cac8ea3","tid":1771643,"uid":65352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"300c8b19f5cf1b29b1bd215254d8846509478258","tid":1771643,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"128"},{"pid":"b07316b28abab79642733f16376c241de50da4f1","tid":1771643,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:11:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9e664526ae93c697e6a97d7ce11b17dd668b18a","tid":1771643,"uid":61493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:18:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"579074943a9d1565e77dac19885e1959c48af4bb","tid":1771643,"uid":284635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"2bdd341689c66240c98006c8bd948875b78522a4","tid":1771643,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"推（1/10）"},{"pid":"e4fd399b4dbb3e4b4a4ad84984c721ad128fe861","tid":1771643,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:45:38.000Z","msg":"推（2/10）"},{"pid":"